 Repent then ! and reform , from the blotting out of your sins , so that there may come times of refreshing from the presence of the Lord ;
66021025	Description	And its gates will not be shut by day , ( For there is no night there ) ;
43006054	Faith	 He who feeds upon my flesh and drinks my blood has eternal life , and I will raise him up on the last day .
